abstracts.cdata!:
The First Highway Project will finance
            part of the construction cost of the Afgoi-Baidoa road (200
            kms) and a feeder road to Uanle Uen (20 kms). The project
            will provide for the completion of construction of a
            two-lane bitumen surfaced road between Afgoi and Baidoa. The
            road will provide all-weather access to an area of
            considerable agricultural potential, the development of
            which is handicapped by inadequate access. The present road
            is closed to traffic, due to water logging, for two to four
            months per year.
